messages.content: Vulpe materialized in Sanguis' mindscape, looking around curiously. "I wonder where Sanguis is...." She hummed and began to walk around, trying to see if she could pick up on his scent

She soon heard footsteps running in her direction, it was indeed Sanguis but....he looked shaken up, “Y-You!” He took a minute to catch his breath, “C-Come with me....**Now!**” he grabbed her arm and ran into a nearby shrine, then the first room he saw, frantically looking around before spotting a closet, and jumping in, he breathes heavily, “here....this should be good enough...” the mun is shaking a little.
"Wh-wha- Sanguis whats going on?!" She was so confused. "Are you ok???? Lovebug please tell me whats going on..." She was worried as wel..

“Shh! Quiet...” he presses his fingers up against his lips, “What happened?.....it’s kind hard to explain-“ he sighs. the door rasps open once again, Sanguis goes tense, “-Stay still!” He harshly whispers 
Humming can be heard
Her tails fluffed up as she heard that and stayed quiet. She...was getting pretty scared now. Shes trying to keep her tails still but its hard.

Footsteps wandered around the room for a bit, “*Kitty~....are you there?”*
**The voice sounded exactly like Sanguis .**

The Sanguis in the closet however looked to vulpe and whispered “Dont open that door...I know-I know.....it *sounds* like me but that....isn’t me....”
2 of her tails had tucked between her legs. Shes pretty scared. The look on her face screaming 'What the fuck'

He noticed...and squeezed her hand in reassurance 
“*I* **know** *that you’re around here.....why are you hiding~? Can it be....that you’re.... afraid of me...? Did that* **Loser** *get to you first~?*” the footsteps continued to wander around, the moving of objects accompanying it.
She smiled a bit at him, squeezing back. Shes staying as still as she can be

“*Why would you be interested in* **him**? *He’s*.....**Weak-**” 
The smashing of a pot.
“-*cant stand....**up for himself**...*”
The tipping of an object, perhaps a chair?
“*And* **I**.....*am everything Sanguis wanted to be~*.....**im not dangerous**” the voice was getting impatient, Sanguis was starting to shake, his fists clenching, either in fear or anger at the things being said, teeth clenched.
Vulpe noticed he was starting to shake and nuzzled him, trying to calm him down.

Once vulpe nuzzled him, his nerves started to calm
“*Are you....under the bed...?*” the bed creaks up, “*no*......**Wait**....”
Sanguis tenses, holding Vulpe tighter.
“*I can hear you......* **Breathing** *from the closet*...”
Footsteps approach the closet, before it’s forcefully opened
“*ah~ there you are~..*” Repluis then sneered, noticing Sanguis 
“*or*.....**Both** *of you are*.”
She goes into her kistune form, growling a bit, getting protective over Sanguis. "Who are you." She growled out

Sanguis puts his hand out in front of her, “Vulpe no-Repluis.....what do you want...?” He sternly asked, in response, the replica laughs, “*Oh~ you remember my name, well...I was wanting to strike a deal-...”*
Vulpe glances between the 2 and sits down for now. Shes ready to jump up and protect Sanguis at any second though.

“*you see....you’ve been with this...love of yours for a while....and it’s made me....feel something....new....I don’t know what it is....but it’s pleasant and I’d...enjoy some time...with her.*”
“**As if I-“**
Repluis holds up a finger “*Ah Ah Ah~ Sanny~*”

"Considering this is about me. I belive I should get a say. And I choose Sanguis. He makes me happy and he loves me." She huffed, putting her head on Sanguis' shoulder, tails swaying a bit, making the bells jingle

His eyes twitched repeatedly as his cocky smile started to falter, “**You....You don’t....want...to be with.....me..?**” he tried to clutch the hole in his chest as voice was wavering, a, at first, heartbroken laugh broiled from his throat
Sanguis eyes widen, as if he knew what was coming, “*kitten....get ready to run...*”
She got on her feet, getting Sanguis on her back. "Hold on tight babe." She said, already in a position to take off running

“**Now!**” he yells as they take off running past Repluis and out of the shrine, hearing his anguished cries devolve into laughter lacking any form of sanity, looking back, Sanguis realized that side of the shrine was completely destroyed with sickly branches growing out of every crevice possible, windows smashed, with the culprit starting to book it after them repeatedly yelling “ ** COME BACK COME BACK COME BACK COME BACK~**” in a unnervingly sing songy voice while insane cackling ensued.
Moriko kept running as fast as she could. As she ran anither Vulpe appeared but more feral looking. FV(that's ehat im gonna nickname her in the mindscape) blinked and began sniffing around.
At first he didn’t notice the second vulpe as he zoomed past her,gaining on his targets, a uncanny wide smile while he bit his lip, the blood dripping down his chin

Vulpe tried to pick up the speed, tails fluffed up as she ran. She was starting to get tired.

FV tilted her head and ran after Repluis, letting out a sort of barking noise.

“I-It’s ok...” he soothingly tells Vulpe “try focusing on zig zagging instead, like me, he’s a clumsy bastard, so he’ll trip or run out of stamina before you do, either way it’ll give us enough time to get away and him enough space to calm down.”

She nodded and began to do so. Her ears twitched as she heard the barks though. "I-I really hope we loose him soon....M-My cracked leg is starting to really hurt....!"

FV had gone into her own kitsune form. She definitely looked smaller then Vulpe thats for sure. She kept barking as she chased

“Don’t worry...just a bit more...” he whispers 
Repluis finally took a glance at the source of the barking and screeched to a halt, doing a triple take, then just kinda...staring at the approaching FV, it’s almost as if his brain is.....lagging? At the sight of **Two** Vulpes, thankfully this gave time for Sanguis and Vulpe to escape

Once they where a safe distance away, Vulpe collapsed onto the ground. Sure enough her cracked leg was glowing a bit

FV tackled Repluis, tails wagging and barking more. She sniffed the other and tilted her head.

Sanguis got off of her, undoing the scarf around his waist and wrapping it around the leg, “I’m so, so sorry kitten..l....I pushed you too hard didn’t I..” 
the replica yelps at being tackled, Landing on his back, stunned, not reacting to the sniffing, just absentmindedly staring up at his captor

She shook her head "Its ok...I think its a combination of the fear and running that made it hurt. Ill be fine, i got 3 other legs to stand on for now" She nuzzled his face and even licked his cheek "Huh.....I heard barking earlier....and....it sounded like a foxes bark....I wonder why..."

FV just started to lick his face.....Like a dog would....She wasnt attacking, thats for sure.

“I heard it too...but it seems he stopped giving chase....so allow me to explain myself ok...?”

Repluis snaps back to his senses, and tries to pry the fox off of him, squirming. Not necessarily uncomfortable....mostly just trying to get up and give chase again.

Vulpe nodded "Alright....Please do..." She hummed

FV Barks again, giving a small growl this time. She....doesnt seem like she want him to go.....Her tails are still wagging as she just....lays on him.....She seems to like his scent...

“That......mun....was created in turn of freeing my mindscape of cracks and monsters.....he was...once me, at my lowest point amplified into a being...Dominus means well, she really does, it just, one of the effects of the amber,” he sighs
Vulpe nodded "Ahh....I see....Well like I said I trust her. I will always be here to help you fight him off ok?" She smiled and nuzzled his cheek a bit
"....Would you perfer to hang out in my mindscape when we are sleeping together??" She asked, tilting her head a bit "Granted....I still have monsters...."

He sighs “Ah, it’s fine,...most of the times he’s just bratty and Annoying, only sometimes he snaps like this......I guess he’s jealous? He hasn’t experienced many emotions yet. Besides, he’s a part of me, I need him, no matter how unstable he is...”
She nodded "Alright." She shifts back into her human form so she can give him a proper kiss on the nose "My legs feeling a bit better....Should we keep moving?"
“No....you should rest a little more, plus....I think he stopped....” he leans against a tree, rubbing his temples in exasperation
She nodded and went back into kitsune form and laid next to him "I wonder what made him stop though..." She hummed in thought
Her ears twitched as she heard the barks again "Thinking about it now.....they sound....like a fox barks......Sanguis are there any foxes in your mindscape other then well, me?" She asked
“Uhm....not that I know of.....” he taps his chin in confusion

"Hm...." She decided to try something, letting out a howling noise

FV ears perked up and she howled back

".....That....sounded identical....pitch and everything...." She was so confused "Wait.....Did....Did I somehow bring out the feral version of me??????" She was so confused and began to pace around trying to figure it out
“I....I don’t.....did you???” Sanguis was now also very confused, clutching his head, “god, what a bizarre day....” he sighs,
She sighed and laid down next to him again "Well.....at least shes keeping him from coming after us for now....."
"Lets...just try and relax while we can..." She placed her head on his lap, sticking out her tounge a bit. She blep
He chuckled, scratching his ear, “that’s adorable....” ruffling her hair
She purred and leaned into it, tails wagging
"I love you so much my lovebug~"
“I love you more kitten~.”
She grins a bit and licks his cheek, waiting to see his response

He flinched and let out a gasp, “Why you-“ Sanguis laughed
Repluis on the other side practically gave up on struggling, grumbles and minor curses escaping his mouth, the branches he summoned being barely affective.

She giggled, licking his face more, tails wagging

FV was now sitting on him, tails wagging as she stared down at him

The mun hugged her tightly, his own tail swaying slightly. 
                                    ……
“What do you want...?” He growled, squirming under her grip, branches trying to either cover him or push her off.

She hugged him back the best she  could in kitsune form before shifting back into mun form and purring happily in the hug.


She barked again, getting into a play bow. She...wants to play with him...
"You know.....I thought of another nickname for you~ Puppy~" Vulpe giggled

“P-Puppy?!” He perks up in surprise, “well....I guess I can’t argue with that...if you’re my kitten......then I’m your puppy..”



Repluis awkwardly brakes off a branch and throws it as hard and far as he could

She kissed his nose, tails wagging

FV takes off fast, running after it.
"I like when we get to cuddle....Its nice..." She smiled, giving him a quick smooch on the lips

He laughs, and leans into it, “Mhm.....the feelings mutual...”

Repluis takes the chance to book it into the Forrest, summoning thick branches to block the path behind him.

She purred happily

FV came running back and saw he left and began to whimper. Her play buddy left her...
Vulpes ears twitch "....Crap....I think we should get going." She goes into her kitsune form. She tries to put pressure on her leg but it still hurts a bit
(Nya
“No, your staying here.” He stands up, summoning Gokuraku,
"I-" she knew she shouldnt argue and so she sat back down, a worried look on her face
“I’ll be fine, I’ve dealt with Repluis many times,” reassurance in his voice as he trails of to the sound of crunching leaves
She nodded and sat there and waited
Meanwhile FV was now howling, sadly

He didn’t have to travel too far, Repluis hovering in the tree, wincing at the howling, a pang in his hole of a chest.....feelings...he didn’t like this one, pushing it back to focus on his new target 
“*Well, well, well, who left the party so early? Too much for you too handle?~*” he sneered
Sanguis stiffened, “**Are-Are you saying that I’m a Coward?**”
“*no, I’m calling you* **Chicken**~” he cackles

Vulpe sighed and checked her leg to make sure it didn't crack anymore. Luckily it hadnt, it just hurt from pushing herself too much.

FV kept howling and whimpering and scratching at branches.
Vulpe is starting to get tired of FVs howling "God....since shes technically me.....I should maybe check up on her...." Vulpe got up and began to walk towards where she heard FV
In Sanguis' mindscape, the goop was starting to try and spread all over

Sanguis himself woke up in a temple
Yet another figure stands on the roof, unamused at the  invasion, *didnt they know that the only monster here should be him?!* with a snap of their fingers the area surrounding the goop explodes with sturdy trees and thorny vines covering it like a impenetrable dome
“**Well, Well, Well, do I have a new play thing?**”
It was suprised and tried to find a way out
It managed to find a few cracks, yet they quickly got sealed as the ever growing dome gets thicker, Repluis climbing down from the building and approaching his work, “Hell~o?”
"Let us out!" It hissed, taking the form of Meriad again

“Nope.....I don’t wanna, I’m always left alone here......”  he whines, before a unhinged laugh replaces it, “**But now**....*heh..heheheh....But now, I won’t be*, **I won’t be alone** because now I have **Y o u**”
It takes the form of Vulpe. "Let. Us. OUT." It hissed
The laughing stopped as he curiously looked at it, a weird substance dripping down from his eyes,
It glared at him, not exactly sure what to do
“Why should I? You’re strange....at first you looked like someone, then another person.....”
"We can look like whatever we want."
“Interesting....You say we, yet I only see one....where are the others..?”
"In others." It shifted its form one by one to look like the muns it had control over. "Meriad is our main host."
“Isn’t it confusing with so many voices? Do they still have their own thoughts...?” He cocks his head to the side, plopping himself down with arms in lap
"We are a hive mind. Our thoughts are mostly one." It explained before copying him "Our thoughts are combined."
“So...the others are thinking what you’re thinking right now....? Would they react at something you experienced in here?” His tail wags
"Yes they are. And why do you ask...." It narrows its eyes
Its getting suspicious of him
“If you’re thinking that I’m going to harm you, don’t waste your breath, it’s been so long since I had a conversation with someone new, and I’m very curious about you~.”
"Then let us out." It huffed "We do not like being trapped."
“You were going to destroy my home....
"No. We weren't. We have no malicious intent. We simply defend if we are attacked...."
“He  told you to stop, yet you didn’t,.....now we’re here....” his tone was getting strained
"All we want is a form to call our own...." It began to explain "Little Aion is helping us....figure stuff out.....she seems to understand...."
“You already have so many, from what I can tell......And I do not know or care about this Aion.,....What I do know is you’re trying to take over *my* body.”
It seemed confused "You are not Sanguis.....How can this be your body if you are not him." It wants to get closer to Repluis

“I....” his breath quivers, “I...used to be....him....I used to be able to feel so many things....to be a entire being....but then....he changed, and I was reduced to a entity residing within....making something leave me....that I can’t remember.... I strain my eyes to find it...sometimes...I strain them so hard....little pieces start to fall off....in desperation I always try to piece them back together.....but they’ll never fit back..never..”. He clutches a side of the dome, “Soon enough....my once pristine...white porcelain eyes have been replaced with warped....ugly ones...”
".....What.....if we could help???" It really didnt know what to do. It...was still getting used to feelings...
“H-How?......how could you possibly help?”
"Well we can allow you control if we make Sanguis sleep..." It proposed
“R-Really?” His expression turns hopeful, but it fades, “No...No it’s too good to be true....how do I know that you aren’t lying, that you won’t take over and leave me here...?”
"Why would we lie? We have no reason to." It hummed
He clenches his fist, “He’s-I’ve heard that so many times....yet there’s still a piece of me...that wants to believe you...”
It put its hand out "You have permission to yank us out if we go back on the deal."
Repluis hesitates, his hand shaking, before some of the branches recede, and takes its hand, “Deal...”
It smiled "We will find Sanguis and make him sleep." And iff it went to look for him
He was just stumbling out of the bed in a main temple....rubbing his temples to get rid of a massive headache
The goop saw him and quickly tried to envelope him.
As a result of the headache....and just getting up, it doesn’t take much force or time before he succumbed.....
"He is sleeping." It called out to Repluis

He eagerly sprinted over, “Let me check....I’ve tried this for a while...he could be faking...” his hand clutches the others head...slamming it onto a nearby table, as the unconscious body drops to the floor, he turns to the goop and gives a thumbs up, “out like a light.” Repluis grins, “Finally....it’s done..”
"What now?" The goop asked, looking at Repluis
“Hmmm..not too sure, I haven’t got this far in....forever...” tapping his foot, he looks around, “Maybe....I should concentrate on possessing?”
It nodded "We will keep him asleep for you."
It seems happy that it did a good job
His grin gets bigger and nods, “is there any particular favor I can do for you?”
"Hmm...We want to learn more about muns. We want to learn their weaknesses...." It hummed "Can you fight a mun for us??"
“Not, a problem~ I could go for a brawl or two....See you on the other side friend.” Repluis does a small salute before his image flickers in an out of being.
It watches with a grin. This is perfect. It likes Repluis.
Vulpe appeared here, looking around for Sanguis. She had to find him.
He is no where to be seen so far, well, not in the open

She starts to sniff around, trying to find him. 

The Goop stands behind Vulpe, a scowl on their face. They try to envelop her and kick her out

Vulpe turned around and jumped back, avoiding the Goop. "Listen- I have no intention to harm you. Just let me get to Sanguis." She growled a bit

"No! We are helping our friend!" They hissed, trying to grab her agian
Vulpe quickly took off running, looking everywhere she could to find Sanguis
Thr Goop give chase

Another pair of footsteps follow them,
Vulpe feels an aura near a temple

She follows it, running as fast as she could. 

The Goop tried to grab her again
Some overgrown branches try and barge the door close, though there was an opening in a window

She jumps in through the window, looking around. 

The Goop follows her and tries to envelop her

Huh, there he was 
Majesticly face planted on the floor, a small amount of blood stained his sliver hair and pooled
She quickly rushed over and shakes him "Puppy- Babe- Wake up-"
It takes a few shakes to get him up, “ugh.......” he blinks a bit, “K.....Kitten....?”

She smiled "Hi!!" However that smile didnt last long as she began to struggle to breathe

Not knowing what else to do, The Goop had used part of themselves to restrict Vulpes ability to breathe
“Shit.” He hissed, trying to pry the goop off of her.

Vulpe clawed at the goop, her tails fluffed up in fear. 

The goop didnt like the feeling of Vulpe clawing at them and retracted, allowing Vulpe to breathe
“We need to get.....out,” he stumbles up, wobbilly, due to the dead injury. Gripping Vulpes arm, “The....Window...”

She took a deep breath, coughing a bit. Once she was able to breathe normally she went into her kitsune form. "Get on my back..." She said, making sure he was able to get on

The Goop was starting to panic a bit. They didnt want to be taken from their friend!!

He was able to sorta.....slump on, clutching his bleeding head.
There’s very rough slams  on the door
"Hold on as tight as you can....I dont want you to fall off..." She said as she took a few steps backwards before taking a running leap out the window
Sanguis tiredly grips her fur as they crash out,
Once out she doesnt stop running. Shes gonna get somewhere safe so Sanguis can recover
The Goop looks at Repluis, unsure of what to do
He looks to them, “they won’t get far.” He growled, snapping his fingers as, A swarm of roots burst from the ground and swerve towards it’s targets

Vulpes ears twitch and she groaned "I didnt want to do this.....But..." She set her feet on fire, making sure it stayed only on her. "Touch me and it will hurt." Vulpe hissed a bit at Repluis

Seeing the fire, Goop held onto Repluis "We....do not like the fire....."
Vulpe was trying to not show it but she was scared...She didnt know what to do...
(Nya?
“Shit, stay here s,” Repluis called the roots to retracted back as he took running
Vulpe saw him start running and took off as well. "Sanguis, Do you know where we can possibly hide??? Im not sure how much running I can do...."
“Forrest......pond.....cove....”  he mumbled out
She nodded and took off into the forest.
She made sure to zig zag as she ran
Sure enough there was a medium  pond....but....no cove to be seen.
"I-I dont see the cove...." Vulpe panted a bit. She was getting tired  but had to keep her energy up so she could help Sanguis
“In....the pond.....” he buried his head into her fur..”In the pond....there’s a......hole....that leads to....a cove...”
"Al-alright...." She jumped into the pond, hoping to find that hole.
It took a small amount of searching to find the big hole carved into the side
She quickly went into it, trying to calm her nerves. God she was....so scared.
Sanguis could probably feel her heart beating really fast...
As she kept swimming, she could feel the water levels lowering, and lowering, until it was only up to her feet, sure enough a small little cave
She sighed in relief and sat down "Y-You ok puppy?" She asked, trying to calm herself
He doesn’t remove himself from his current position but give a thumbs up.

She smiled a bit and gently nuzzled him. God she loved him so much...."Hm.....I have an idea. Perhaps we could trap the goop in your mindscape? I think its a hivemind....We could make it help us find the others...." Vulpe hummed
Still a bit out of it, he tilts his head,”Huh...? How.....could we...with Repluis?”

"Maybe strike a deal with him? He has called the goop his friend and I dont think he would take to kindly to the goop leaving.....Perhaps in return for its help, the goop is allowed to stay? I dont think its really going to do harm...." She tilted her head a bit
(Nya
“That......sounds...like it could work...” he mumbled
She smiled at that, tails wagging "Alright....Now let me see your head injury..." She hummed "We should probably clean it up ..:
(Nya
He groans, “Nooooo, no no, I’m fine....it’s just a....scratch...nothin...bad.” Sanguis covered his head with both arms,

She got suspicious of that. She shifted into her mun form, gently taking his face in her hands "Sanguis. Puppy. Love of my life. I love you and care about you but I will not hesitate to pin you down in order to see your injury." She hummed
A pouty whine escapes,as he leans into her touch, “But.....I’m fine.......I’m really fine........”
"Then just let me see it...Please?" Shes about to pull out her puppy dog eyes
She gently kisses his nose, tails wagging a small bit

*curses! How dare she know his weaknesses!*. “Hnnngh....fine....don’t be upset or I’m....gonna be upset...” he removed his hands and...yikes...his arms seemed stained red along with the front part of hair.

She sighed "Lets get this cleaned up...." She took some fabric off of her long coat and let it get wet in some of the water in the cave. She then gently began to clean that area up so she could get a better look at it "Hmmm~ You look cute with a bit of red hair~" She giggled, trying to lighten the mood a bit
After a while she finished cleaning the wound "There....its clean now...Hmm....I dont have a bandage though...."
, “Ow ow ow....”  he squirmed......but the small comment made him blush,

"Hmmm....if I dyed a bit of my hair would you do a bit of yours? I think it would be cute...." she hummed, taking off her coat and taking a longer peice of fabric off from the back and using it as a makeshift bandage "There.....That should be fine..."
She gently kisses his wrapped injury, tails wagging
"Do you just wanna just cuddle for a bit?"
“Mmhhhmm..” he quickly rests his head in the crook of Vulpes neck
She purred loudly, tails wagging. God she loved him so much....
"Mmmm I love you so much.....Im so happy to be with you...."
(Do u wanna timeskip?
(Yee);
~After a while of cuddling and being cute~

"Mmmm....Puppy as much as I love this. I think its time we put our plan into action. You are....currently on the beach. Where a siren resides. I dont want her trying to hurt you....Meanwhile I......am currently in your body technically. I had to use my ability to possess others to come here...." She rubbed her arm a bit. She seemed nervous telling him that "Its....an ability i hardly ever use..."
“Y-Yeah.....but how do we get him to listen....he’s a stubborn bastard......eh..like me...” he deadpans
She thought a bit "Hmm.....Perhaps....Perhaps he'll listen to me. He seems to like me. So maybe hes willing to listen!" She hummed "And the goop, perhaps they can convince him as well."
“Hmmm, sounds good...let’s...hope it goes well.” Sanguis stretches
She goes back into her kitsune form, tails swaying a bit. She was going to have to swim through water again....
Should....she tell him?? She glanced at Sanguis, thinking abiut it
He started to walk towards the entrance, “You coming?”
"Y-yeah...." She followed after him
“I think I can swim on my own.” He sighs, “On the count of three?” He turns around to face Vulpe
She tried to hide the look of fear on her face and nodded
“Do you, want....to hold my hand?.” Outstretching an arm, he gives a small, sheepish, smile
She went into her mun form and nodded, taking his hand, a small blush on her face
"Alright....lets go...."
“Mhm.”
And off they go!!!! Vulpe is doing her best to not let her fear get to her
Sanguis can probably feel her hand shaking
He wasn’t able to see her clearly or talk, so instead he gave her hand a tight squeeze, the surface wasn’t too far up.
She felt reassured, happy to see the surface coming up
Soon enough their heads emerged from the water, “Phew!” Sanguis gave a breath of relief
Vulpe took a deep breath, trying to stop herself for shaking "N-Not....doing that again....."
After a while she regains her composure "Al-alright ..Lets go...."

He was still shaky from the water, but there was no time to be wasted! “...yeah...but...where would Repluis b-“ a snapping of a twig alerts him
“.........**He’s right behind me isn’t he..**”
Vulpe goes into defense mode "Repluis dont attack. I have a proposition to make so hear me out." Shes pulled Sanguis behind her

“*and why should I?*” he growled 
“Rep for once in your life don’t be a uncooperative bitc-“ Sanguis harshly whispers before covering his mouth, *don’t poke the bear*

"Because I think its a good idea. Now the idea is this, Sanguis allows the goop to stay here in return for them helping us find the others who are possessed. The goop is a hive mind yes? Then they should be able to help find the others. I think its a win win. You get to keep your friend and the others are freed." She said, tails flicking a bit

Goop, who was close behind Repluis, seemed to brighten up at that idea.
He looks from Vulpe to Goop, a in-thought expression, “?....How do I know I can trust you?”

"Because I dont go back on deals." She placed a hand over her heart "I promise that I wont go back on the deal. Sanguis, You make a promise as well...."

Goops tail was wagging a bit "We like this deal. We can separate ourselves from the hivemind after we help! And we get to stay with our friend!"
(Nya
“Hmmmm....I suppose that deal sounds....satisfactory..” he huffed, looking to the side,

"We accept your deal!" Goop hummed happily

Vulpe smiled "Thats good to know..."
“Soo....” Sanguis awkwardly looks around, “....now what..?”

"Im going to leave your body so you can wake up. We should head back to the temple after this and I'll contact Radium and we can go from there..." Vulpe hummed, gently kissing Sanguis on the nose before giving a pat on the head to Repluis.
“Yeah, we should.....uh, bye? I guess?” He awkwardly gives a small wave to the two entities. Though the only response from Repluis was narrowed eyes.

Vulpe vanishes from the mindscape as she leaves Sanguis' body

".....The others have been named...Momo....its a stupid name...." Goop huffed a bit, looking at Repluis

Sanguis follows suit
“Momo? The hell is that even supposed to mean?” He looks back, confused.
"Its a name....We dont like it...." they hummed "Hey....How about you give us a better name?"
